public int[] computeLevelChanges(TreeAnalyzer.PivotLevels previous)
Compute the (most shallow) level at which this path changes from the previous. null indicates that there is no level change result[0] indicates the (explicit) section level to end (0 for none) result[1..n] indicates the division levels to start (implied divisions and sections to end).
